1
00:00:44,102 --> 00:00:47,076
Colonel Dubaku, we are just
leaving the township now, sir.

2
00:00:47,201 --> 00:00:49,149
- How many do you have?
- Five.

3
00:00:50,033 --> 00:00:52,199
- Only five?
- By the time we got to the field,

4
00:00:52,324 --> 00:00:55,845
- most of the boys were gone.
- I need soldiers, not excuses.

5
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:58,181
I will bring some more, sir, I promise.

6
00:00:58,576 --> 00:00:59,808
Just bring them to me.

7
00:01:15,493 --> 00:01:17,242
You will learn to fight like men.

8
00:01:17,726 --> 00:01:19,529
Of that, I have no doubt.

9
00:01:21,242 --> 00:01:22,269
This...

10
00:01:22,867 --> 00:01:24,886
will make you strong, little soldiers.

11
00:01:26,993 --> 00:01:28,545
This will make you free.

12
00:01:33,172 --> 00:01:34,172
Come.

13
00:01:36,313 --> 00:01:37,313
Take it.

14
00:01:41,868 --> 00:01:43,455
How does it make you feel?

15
00:01:45,172 --> 00:01:46,239
Powerful, yes?

16
00:01:50,740 --> 00:01:51,740
Come.

17
00:01:55,909 --> 00:01:57,782
Your mothers and your fathers...

18
00:01:58,116 --> 00:01:59,771
they have made you weak,

19
00:02:00,549 --> 00:02:01,895
but General Juma...

20
00:02:02,378 --> 00:02:03,895
he will make you strong.

21
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:06,134
He will make you strong

22
00:02:06,259 --> 00:02:08,793
so you can take back the country
from the government

23
00:02:09,517 --> 00:02:11,967
and the traitors that work for them...

24
00:02:12,185 --> 00:02:14,074
like this cockroach here!

25
00:02:23,872 --> 00:02:25,185
This cockroach

26
00:02:25,396 --> 00:02:28,856
who works for the government
and their white masters...

27
00:02:32,309 --> 00:02:34,201
They have taken our land.

28
00:02:38,869 --> 00:02:41,113
But soon, all that will change.

29
00:02:41,748 --> 00:02:45,163
Soon, all the land
will belong to the people again.

30
00:02:46,939 --> 00:02:47,939
Soldier...

31
00:02:49,795 --> 00:02:53,401
you must buy our freedom
with the blood of this cockroach.

32
00:02:57,553 --> 00:02:59,677
And you know what we do to cockroaches.

33
00:03:00,506 --> 00:03:01,916
Kill the cockroach.

34
00:03:02,558 --> 00:03:04,008
Kill the cockroach!

35
00:03:38,624 --> 00:03:41,012
Episode 7x00
"Redemption"

36
